 foods like sausage and jerky, make it as versatile as it is efficient.</p></div><div class="MuiBox-root css-tynld3" data-og-block-area="article-blocks" data-og-block-nth="12" data-og-block-type="core/heading" id="h-most-versatile-weber-original-kettle-grill"><div class="MuiContainer-root MuiContainer-maxWidthXl MuiContainer-disableGutters css-mj8i10"><h3 class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-h4 css-1w029u5" data-rawhtml="1"><strong>Most Versatile: <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00MKB5TXA/?tag=sav-best-smoker-20">Weber Original Kettle Grill</a></strong></h3></div></div><div class="MuiBox-root css-tynld3" data-og-block-area="article-blocks" data-og-block-nth="13" data-og-block-type="core/heading" id=""><div class="MuiContainer-root MuiContainer-maxWidthXl MuiContainer-disableGutters css-mj8i10"><h5 class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-h6 css-1ph1f9b" data-rawhtml="1"><em>Material: Porcelain | Max temp: 600 F | Hopper capacity: N/A | Power source: None | Fuel type: Charcoal</em></h5></div></div><div class="MuiBox-root css-0" data-og-block-area="article-blocks" data-og-block-nth="6" data-og-block-type="acf/product-card"><h2 class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-h3 categorySectionTitle css-dvsykq"></h2><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container css-1ibpig5"><div class="MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-item MuiGrid-grid-xs-5 css-znshj7"><img alt="" loading="lazy" src="https://www.saveur.com/uploads/2021/06/23/The-Best-Smoker-Option-Weber-Original-Kettle-Grill.jpg?auto=webp&amp;auto=webp&amp;optimize=high&amp;quality=70&amp;width=1440" style="max-width:100%;width:100%;display:block;height:100%;aspect-ratio:1;object-fit:cover" srcSet="
